These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
House: wooden, ranch-style
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, brown
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| House       | ranch-style    | wooden    |
| Color   | brown       | turquise      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
House: palace, colonial
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, train
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the palace house is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| House           | palace | colonial      |
| Transport   | train  | scooter      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, superhero
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the thai is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | romance | superhero  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Nationality   | thai  | chinese   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, may
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar
1. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Birthday          | may         | september    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Cigar   | swisher           | bolivar   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, nurse
2 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country       |
| Job         | journalist   | nurse |
| Pet     | rabbit    | ferret     |

