The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball
City: miami, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Cigar           | chaman  | swisher   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | salsa      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| City     | marseilles     | miami |

