.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, october
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
There 2 different types of food: spinach, zucchini
1. the coach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Birthday   | december          | october |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Food     | zucchini            | spinach       |

 